{
  "text": "The Australian Genomics Manager had the highest in-degree, out-degree and brokerage score. As found in other similar networks [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , the manager's role in a number of different working groups and Flagship projects makes them highly visible and knowledgeable about the whole alliance.",
